The 2010 BRIT Awards show is destined to be the biggest show yet. Celebrating 30 years of the awards, the show will feature a host of the worlds biggest stars with Peter Kaye playing host to the event. This 3-CD compilation contains 2 discs of the biggest tracks of 2009 including Lady Gaga, Cheryl Cole, JLS and Robbie Williams with a bonus third disc of exclusive, never-before released collaborations and some of the biggest classic BRIT Award winners of all time!
